reviewText: Got this for some wedding inspiration for my upcoming nuptials. DVD runs well, it has different episodes which you can watch from the menu page. I loved this series years ago and it has been so hard to find but now I have some we can watch for fun
Very good buy for the price! This DVD comes with 18 episodes. I plan to use this to get inspiration while planning my own wedding.
Every little girls dream!!! Love Platinum Weddings!!!

A WONDERFUL HELP TOOL FOR ALL BRIDES TO BE!! EVEN IF THEY CAN'T
AFFORD IT, I'M SURE THEY FOUND SOME IDEAS THAT WILL MAKE THEM
VERY VERY HAPPY!!
